(981, 'EX-562072', 'FB', '<p>ANSWER ANY THREE QUESTIONS OF YOUR CHOICE THEORY</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Outline the names of the twelve disciples of Jesus Christ (6mks)</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>1b. State four reasons Why Jesus Called The Disciples (4mks)</p>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"2\">\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>State any five factors that affect true discipleship (5mks)</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>2b. State the five rules and regulations that guides the operations of the Sanhedrin (5mks)</p>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"3\">\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>A. Write down the seven words of Jesus on the cross (7mks)</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>B. state any three Bible passages any of these words can be found (3mks)</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a name=\"_GoBack\"></a>4a. What is temptation ?(2mks)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>4b. State six significance of the temptation of Jesus(6mks)</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '-', '-', '-', '-', '-', '', ''),
